# WebScreenshots

20000 Web pages (URLs, text contents, screenshots in 1440x900 and 224x224) seperated into 4 classes upon their visual appearance (screenshots). Dataset created in the second quarter of 2019.

# Download 1440x900 sized screenshots
You can download 1440x900 sized screenshots from: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1RUTXO0nJLbmDPIO8h6aixhVyuhmvT7VB

# Please make a citation
If you want to use WebScreenshots dataset, please make a citation:
```
@data{aydos2020,
  title={WebScreenshots},
  url={https://www.kaggle.com/ds/202248},
  DOI={10.34740/KAGGLE/DS/202248},
  publisher={Kaggle},
  author={Fahri Aydos},
  year={2020}
}
```

# Academic papers that used WebScreenshots

- Web page classification with Google Image Search results
